{"article_id":"TzoMHgO9FJNRIYxa","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"When Christine Blasey Ford said","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"she could not remember certain details about her alleged assault by Brett Kavanaugh ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"Rep. Ann McLane Kuster could relate .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"The New Hampshire Democrat says","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"she experienced something similar","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"after she was sexually assaulted some 40 years ago .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Like Ford , Kuster ca n't pinpoint the exact date of the event .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"But the two women say","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"they remember other aspects of the incident vividly .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Ford told the Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"she is `` 100 % '' certain","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Kavanaugh assaulted her ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"while Kuster has said","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"that she will never forget her assailant ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"whom she has described as `` a classmate","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"egged on by his fraternity brothers . ''","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"After vehemently denying the allegations ,","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Kavanaugh is n ow the newest justice on the Supreme Court .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"But Capitol Hill is still grappling with the fallout from the divisive confirmation fight and an outpouring of personal stories from constituents and fellow lawmakers","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"who shared accounts of their own experiences of sexual assault .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"In the midst of incendiary partisanship","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"surrounding the blockbuster congressional hearings and historically tight confirmation vote ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Republican and Democratic women alike spoke about how they and women close to them have been affected by sexual misconduct .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Some women , like Ford , described events","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"they said","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"took place decades ago .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"Others publicly acknowledged for the first time","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"that they have had # MeToo experiences ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"while declining to specify what happened .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"The accounts of women","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"who came forward","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"to tell their stories during the confirmation fight","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"shaped the conversation","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that unfolded on Capitol Hill ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"though it may be months or even years","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"before it is clear what the lasting effect will be on Congress from the outcome of the Kavanaugh hearings and the decision of so many women","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"to speak about their experiences with sexual violence .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Democratic Rep. Debbie Dingell ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"who has spoken about her own # MeToo experiences in the past ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"said in an interview","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"that women in the congressional district","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"she represents in Michigan","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"told her heart-wrenching personal stories in the midst of the Kavanaugh confirmation .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"`` So many people had stories ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"it was unbelievable , ''","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"The congresswoman said","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that she was in Ann Arbor , Michigan on the day","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"the Senate voted to elevate Kavanaugh to the Supreme Court","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"when a woman came up to her","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"and started sobbing .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"The woman said","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"that her sister had committed suicide years ago after a sexual assault .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"The Michigan Democrat has also heard from men in her district","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"who have confided in her about their own fears and anxieties over the current cultural reckoning over harassment and assault .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"`` I ca n't tell you the number of men now","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"who tell me","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"they 're just not going to hire women","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"because they say","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"it 's too complicated , ''","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"Dingell said .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"`` People are scared .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"... I think","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"men are worried","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"that their lives are going to be destroyed . ''","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"The challenge now ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"the Democratic congresswoman says ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"is to figure out how to deal with unacceptable behavior","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"so that `` women are n't hurt in the progress","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"being made in the workplace , ''","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"while at the same time `` making sure","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"that due process is being preserved . ''","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"The same day","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"Ford testified ,","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"five Democratic congresswomen sent a letter to President Donald Trump and Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"identifying themselves as domestic and sexual assault victims","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"and calling for votes on the nomination to be postponed and an investigation into allegations against Kavanaugh .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"whom had spoken","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"The letter was signed by Kuster and Dingell as well as Reps. Jackie Speier of California , Gwen Moore of Wisconsin and Alma Adams of North Carolina ,","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"all of publicly about experiences of harassment , assault or domestic violence prior to the confirmation fight .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"It was n't just Democratic lawmakers","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"who made reference to # MeToo moments in their own lives","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"as the confirmation fight played out .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"An Alaska Public Media reporter asked Republican Sen. Lisa Murkowski","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"if she had ever had a # MeToo moment .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"The Alaskan senator replied","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"that she had ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"saying `` yes , ''","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"though she did not elaborate further .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"In the end , Murkowski was the lone GOP senator","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"to oppose Kavanaugh 's nomination .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"The senator said","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"she believes","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"Kavanaugh is a `` good man '' in a speech","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"explaining her decision ,","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"but said","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"she `` could not conclude","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"that he is the right person for the court at this time . ''","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"Separately , White House counselor Kellyanne Conway , a Kavanaugh defender , revealed during an interview with CNN 's Jake Tapper","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"that she is a victim of sexual assault .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"Conway suggested , however ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"that people","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"who are not responsible for sexual misconduct","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"unfairly became targets of blame","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"as the confirmation battle became intensely politicized .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"`` Let 's just be honest what this is about .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"It 's raw partisan politics , ''","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"she said ,","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"discussing the Kavanaugh fight .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"In other instances , some women in Congress shared stories of women","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"close to them","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"who have been affected by assault .","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"A few days after announcing","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"she opposed the Kavanaugh nomination ,","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"Democratic Sen. Heidi Heitkamp of North Dakota told The New York Times","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"that her mother was a victim of sexual assault .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"Heitkamp has since become embroiled in controversy","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"and has issued an apology","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"after her campaign misidentified some women as survivors of abuse in an ad .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"Congress , over the last year , has faced # MeToo moments of its own .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"A number of lawmakers on both sides of the aisle were forced to resign in the past year","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"after women came forward with misconduct allegations ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"shining a spotlight on the need","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"for Congress to get its own house in order","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"for how sexual harassment claims are made and handled on Capitol Hill .","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"Earlier this year , the House and Senate passed their own versions of bills","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"to overhaul the process ,","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"but lawmakers still have yet to reach a final deal ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"leading to criticism from advocates for reform over the long-stalled legislation","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"Republican Sen. John Kennedy , a Kavanaugh supporter","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"who sits on the Judiciary Committee","depth":15},{"id":132,"text":"which vetted Kavanaugh 's nomination ,","depth":15},{"id":133,"text":"said","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"that hearing personal stories from women `` drives home the point","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"that sexual violence is prevalent in America ''","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"and said","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"that the # MeToo movement had opened his eyes to the extent of the problem .","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"`` I did n't realize","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"how prevalent it was","depth":14},{"id":140,"text":"until the MeToo movement started , ''","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"the Louisiana senator said .","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"`` I 've talked to friends of mine","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"who happen to be women","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"and they say ,","depth":15},{"id":145,"text":"'what planet did you just parachute in from ,","depth":15},{"id":146,"text":"this has been going on forever , ' ''","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"he added .","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"Kennedy said ,","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"`` I 'm not saying","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"I never saw anything ,","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"but I just had no idea ,","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"and I 'm convinced","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"it 's real .","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"And I understand the reluctance","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"to speak up .","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"And I think","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"we 've got to deal with it .","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"But I do n't think","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"you deal with it","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"by throwing out due process . ''","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"Democratic Sen. Mazie Hirono , an opponent of the Kavanaugh nomination and also a member of the Senate Judiciary Committee , described the confirmation process as `` a galvanizing moment","depth":13},{"id":162,"text":"for so many people to come forward . ''","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"The Hawaii senator said","depth":15},{"id":164,"text":"that several close friends","depth":17},{"id":165,"text":"she has known for a long time","depth":17},{"id":166,"text":"recently confided in her about their own experiences of rape and sexual assault .","depth":16},{"id":167,"text":"`` So many women came forward","depth":16},{"id":168,"text":"and told us their accounts","depth":17},{"id":169,"text":"that they had never shared before , ''","depth":17},{"id":170,"text":"Hirono said .","depth":15},{"id":171,"text":"`` This was a moment","depth":15},{"id":172,"text":"for them","depth":16},{"id":173,"text":"to come forward","depth":17},{"id":174,"text":"to be heard ,","depth":17},{"id":175,"text":"and I know","depth":15},{"id":176,"text":"they were hoping to be believed . ''","depth":15},{"id":177,"text":"After Ford testified before Congress ,","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"President Donald Trump mocked her at a rally ,","depth":14},{"id":179,"text":"repeatedly saying ,","depth":16},{"id":180,"text":"`` I do n't remember , ''","depth":16},{"id":181,"text":"in imitation of the fact","depth":16},{"id":182,"text":"that she could not recall every detail of the alleged event .","depth":16},{"id":183,"text":"`` 'How did you get home ?","depth":16},{"id":184,"text":"I do n't remember .","depth":16},{"id":185,"text":"How 'd you get there ?","depth":17},{"id":186,"text":"I do n't remember .","depth":17},{"id":187,"text":"Where is the place ?","depth":18},{"id":188,"text":"I do n't remember .","depth":18},{"id":189,"text":"How many years ago was it ?","depth":18},{"id":190,"text":"I do n't know , ' ''","depth":18},{"id":191,"text":"Trump said to cheers and applause .","depth":14},{"id":192,"text":"After vehemently denying the allegations against him ,","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"Kavanaugh went on to be confirmed along a party-line vote by the Senate","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"with one Democrat voting for his nomination","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"after Senate Republicans argued","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":"that an FBI investigation found no corroborating evidence","depth":14},{"id":197,"text":"to substantiate allegations against him .","depth":14},{"id":198,"text":"Dingell worries","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"that women may be more reluctant to come forward","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"after seeing how Ford was treated and how","depth":13},{"id":201,"text":"despite her allegations ,","depth":14},{"id":202,"text":"Kavanaugh was still confirmed to the Supreme Court .","depth":14},{"id":203,"text":"`` Part of the problem for a woman is that","depth":15},{"id":204,"text":"when she comes forward ...","depth":15},{"id":205,"text":"you get branded ,","depth":14},{"id":206,"text":"you 're a troublemaker , ''","depth":13},{"id":207,"text":"she said ,","depth":12},{"id":208,"text":"adding ,","depth":12},{"id":209,"text":"`` I have stories","depth":14},{"id":210,"text":"I wo n't tell to this day ,","depth":14},{"id":211,"text":"if I were to tell the stories","depth":14},{"id":212,"text":"they would have major implications","depth":15},{"id":213,"text":"that I 'm just unwilling to share . ''","depth":15},{"id":214,"text":"Kuster says","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"she found it painful to watch Ford recount her allegations in front of members of Congress ,","depth":10},{"id":216,"text":"but she also believes","depth":10},{"id":217,"text":"that the California professor 's decision","depth":12},{"id":218,"text":"to testify publicly","depth":12},{"id":219,"text":"will ultimately help survivors .","depth":11},{"id":220,"text":"`` People are often inhibited from coming forward","depth":11},{"id":221,"text":"and by the time","depth":14},{"id":222,"text":"they do have the courage","depth":14},{"id":223,"text":"to tell their story","depth":13},{"id":224,"text":"they might not have all of the details at hand , ''","depth":12},{"id":225,"text":"the congresswoman said .","depth":10},{"id":226,"text":"`` She was able to articulate the way","depth":12},{"id":227,"text":"people feel","depth":13},{"id":228,"text":"when they have these glimpses of memory , ''","depth":13},{"id":229,"text":"Kuster said ,","depth":11},{"id":230,"text":"adding ,","depth":12},{"id":231,"text":"`` That 's a very common experience for anyone","depth":14},{"id":232,"text":"experiencing trauma","depth":14},{"id":233,"text":"and in particular for survivors of sexual assault ...","depth":13},{"id":234,"text":"so I think","depth":12},{"id":235,"text":"what she said was very important in our continuing effort","depth":13},{"id":236,"text":"to educate the public . ''","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":473,"left":0,"right":472,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":472,"left":308,"right":471,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":254,"right":307,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":252,"right":253,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":245,"right":251,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":242,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":239,"right":241,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":239,"left":238,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":238,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":241,"left":4,"right":240,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":240,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":7,"right":243,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":243,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":251,"left":247,"right":250,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":247,"left":10,"right":246,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":246,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":250,"left":13,"right":249,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":249,"left":14,"right":248,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent"